Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not one person arrived at a place like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you seek such a place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't you let this go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'd known it was all a dream. Why didn't you acknowledge that it's a dream?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Iskandar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hephaestion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten over the worst of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Looks like he failed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have good skills, contrary to what I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is healing magic your forte?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My forte or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he taught me Electrical Magecraft several weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Several weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors about the El-Melloi Classroom, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A Servant attacked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomenon of summoning a Heroic Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with its original personality intact
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,can't possibly happen outside the Holy Grail War in Fuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Invocation."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A spell enabling you to project Heroic Spirits and Divine Spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,onto yourself, so that you can borrow their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to invoke the god of manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,would you become good at drawing manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why does it have to be manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The author of the manga I bought recently at the used bookstore is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to read the continuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In principle, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Harboring the soul of the deceased on yourself in an attempt to artificially revive that soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you call "Sibyl's Magecraft."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Many sibyls who have high affinity to astral bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are unaware of their links to memories and consciousness of such bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a divine possession just like Animalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you materialize the Heroic Spirit or Divine Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and let them go on a manga drawing spree?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just say that it's not impossible theoretically,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but securing enough magical energy to support such a spell is unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, about invocation in practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the example of\NNative American faith in Power Animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was without a doubt a\NHeroic Spirit who has materialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Such power can't be that of a magus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the more reason she has something to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was a Servant, there should be a Master who summoned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:42.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps she was the one who murdered Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical energy needs to be supplied to summoned Heroic Spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hephaestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the primary confidante of the greatest King of Conquerors in history, Iskandar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how she introduced herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A Heroic Spirit who was even dubbed "the other Iskandar"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It all clicks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys didn't come aboard this train to buy Mystic Eyes, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A Lord who has no interest in the auction,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the King of Conquerors who once was his minion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the subject who attacked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. So, Iskandar's relic has been stolen from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That about sum it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Trisha said, this Lord is fixated on the King of Conquerors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a Heroic Spirit who is regarded in the same way as Iskandar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you can summon her from the King of Conquerors' relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that also mean that her Master is aboard this train, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That is quite likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But about Hephaestion, it's the opposite of normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposite? What is opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, Servants hide True Names when possible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because they expose their weaknesses and abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, they're usually called by the class that the Heroic Spirit is designated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,like "Saber" and "Lancer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we know the True Name, but we don't know the class, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sir Rodin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an anomaly in the train's path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hard to believe, but someone meddled with the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This train is headed toward the Child of Ainnash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we throttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The output won't go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing less from my old haunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Premonition is only a prediction,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't see through incidents with nothing leading up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We have an announcement to all passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I regret to inform you that this train has entered the Child of Ainnash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainnash?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding! The Forest of Dead Apostles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're sorry for the inconvenience until we resume course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But we ask that each passenger secure their own safety in the meanwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to check outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die? Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This forest is screwing up the leyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O noble spirit materializing the great desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to burn off the forest that the rails are heading into.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But if something like that can have any effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Receive our guidance and show the flames of origin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they call it the "Forest of Dead Apostles,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a byproduct severed from the main body. This should—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They strike in reaction to attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put up a bounded field and barricade myself in until the situation is resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be! We can combine forces to escape or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know who killed Trisha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And doing something about this forest in a situation like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It would only create more corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you this! I'm not your ally or anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sufficient by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Olga Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Trisha properly taught me so that I could do things by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, are you able to protect your mentor through all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean-Mario Spinella's Zombie Cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, let's enjoy cooking whole roasted zombies together with Jean-Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And the curtain falls on Zombie Cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great, Jean-Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this person really versed in the affairs of the Clock Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let me introduce you, Luvia, to Jean-Mario Spinella.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an old acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, young lady. Anything regarding the media and gourmet is my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, how about a meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lean dry-aged meat with a perfectly seasoned sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I added a bit of soy sauce in the Madeira for the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Soy sauce is good and all, but can I get to the heart of the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the case seven years ago where many headless corpses were found in London?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No magus who meddles with the media would be ignorant of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A murder using the same tactic happened on the Mystic Eyes Collection Train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, there were seven victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all said to have been holders of Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't recall such an incident being on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Clock Tower put on some pressure, and so did the Holy Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In the media, it was limited to one or two broadcasts on local stations,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tapes of those broadcasts have been seized by the Clock Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the case ever resolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, the case has been settled as a result of joint investigation with the Holy Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it because I got the info from a friend in Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is this case booming right now or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl from Astromancy wanted to hear about it just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we ask you what her name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Trisha Fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as cold as Siberia outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long we can last with the heating equipment on this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems fine for now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I heard that Waver was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came by helicopter to watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but a forest suddenly spawned, and I got engulfed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still an idiot as he's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There surely are many easier ways of life for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one thing, Miss Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who injured Waver this badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who other than myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you are busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You need us to lend a hand to move this train?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Regretfully, we must now think about the possibility of canceling the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, I can't extract these Mystic Eyes until the next auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we want our little apprentice and Caules to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bit of knowledge about this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This location is a topic of conversation in the Holy Church, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Holy Church?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainnash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest is a thinking, preying organism, said to perhaps be a Reality Marble
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,controlled by a high-ranking Dead Apostle of the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can find the main leylines,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and sink in a few guide markers from our end, we can activate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And by doing that, we should be able to move the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But most of the magi are barricading themselves in their compartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That snake lady from Policies refused, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so obstinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The more people we have, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Master will not last being exposed to this cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Leave Professor to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, can I mingle with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I may look like this, but I'm a tuner of magic crests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be the Melvin Waynes!\NThe legendary tuner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We stand a good chance with this many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My body feels warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The sounds are resonating with our magic circuits and activating them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I improved your magic circuits by about 20 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be of some use, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I go all out in order to witness amusing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll detect all the other leylines altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm feeling really good thanks to the tuning,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to find at least two more pressure points for the leylines. Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Add?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad, bad, bad! The bad thing is looking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, little apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, ahead of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'll make sure to catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds amusing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you noticed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Add...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, I thought things might end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate that the narrow-minded man is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you assault Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it was because I didn't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, you must have some other reason you lured him out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you can get it out of me with that blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You stand on the battleground not to fight, but to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why do you have that blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't surrender to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to speak as equals and have you return the relic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So, that's your resolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that previous guidepost has marked us as intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yvette's Processed Mystic Eyes,\NBurning Flame Version!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The next response is from the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A large rock at one o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought warriors were extinct in this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have good potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your glimmer is trying to cling onto life,\Nsomewhere between life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain that Master is going through has a lot more value than anything like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you shall give it all you've got for your loyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm at my limit soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sliding down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why we say the Holy Church is barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels like a roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There, in the center of the vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a response! The leyline is activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is strange. It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A spell right on these coordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the floor or the ceiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was embedded in the relative coordinates from the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,someone like that despicable Lord would've long since found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reacting to my magic crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell is of the Fellows family that branched out from Animusphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A dimensional pocket with an Imaginary attribute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, the password should open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Silly Little Marie, straighten yourself out."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange! This is strange! What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Trisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Was someone watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm glad. You found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing less from the heir of the Animusphere name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Miss Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! I didn't think you could cross swords with me this well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Likely beyond the boundaries of ordinary men!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worthy of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An avalanche?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was simply a divided piece of a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With the domination of the leyline taken away,\Nit's become unbearable quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? If you don't escape, you'll die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let you escape here, Master will be hurt! That, if nothing else...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Add!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First Stage, Rescind Restraints!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we have no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How well you bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:10.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
